T9. URL download — rapid double-click guard (Bug 1, post-Phase-A)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    Added 2026-05-12 alongside the add_url concurrency guard.
    Click "🌐 Add URL", paste any URL, click OK to start a batch.
    While the progress dialog is visible, click the (now-disabled)
    "🌐 Add URL" button several times.
    Verify: button is visibly disabled and does not open the dialog
            again.
    Bypass attempt (optional): if you can fire the slot via a custom
    keyboard shortcut or accessibility tool, do so. The defensive
    QMessageBox "A URL download is already in progress" should appear
    instead of a second dialog.
    Wait for the batch to finish (or cancel it).
    Verify: button becomes enabled again.
    OUTCOME:   [N]   notes: not run — added with the Bug 1 fix on
